          'We will tweak your operations and tooling to maximize program efficiency. Whether you need a full overhaul or just a few tweaks, we can help.',
        icon: 'tabler:settings',
      },
      {
        title: 'Collaborative Selling',
        description:
          'Ready to start selling with your partners? We can help you build a collaborative selling program that will help you close more deals.',
        icon: 'tabler:heart-handshake',
      },
      {
        title: 'Onboarding Strategy',
        description:
          'We will help you build a partner onboarding strategy that will help you get your partners up and running quickly, while providing a great experience.',
        icon: 'tabler:arrow-ramp-left',
      },
      {
        title: 'Attribution Analytics',
        description:
          'Is your attribution a black box? We can help you build a custom attribution model that will help you understand the true ROI of your partner program.',
        icon: 'tabler:dashboard',
      },
      {
        title: 'Account Mapping',
        description:
          "We'll help you build a program that will help you map your partner's accounts to your own, so you can get the most out of your partner relationships.",
        icon: 'tabler:compass',
      },
      {
        title: 'Experience-led Relationships',
        description:
          'We will help plan experiences that will keep your partners engaged and excited about your program. Let us handle that planning, so you can  just execute.',
        icon: 'tabler:bulb',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    tagline="Why Uppercut"
    title="Uppercut's Blueprint: Your Fractional PSM"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Engineering + Partner Success',
        description:
          'Reap the benefits of a team that has a deep understanding of the technical aspects of partnerships, as well as the operational side.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Engaging in Ecosystems',
        description:
          'We always do everything we can to learn about our clients ecosystem, so we can provide the most value possible.',
      },
      {
        title: 'A Bit Client Obsessed',
        description:
          'We are always looking for new ways to up the ante on our client experience, and we go feral for providing value.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3900437/pexels-photo-3900437.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2',
      alt: 'Colorful Image',
    }}
  >
